videos.description: Terell Smith undercuts a pass from Marcus McMaryion to set up the Golden Gophers in Fresno State territory.
videos.headline: Minnesota DB jumps in front for INT

videos.description: WR Seth Green follows his blockers and crosses the goal-line to put the Golden Gophers up 7-0.
videos.headline: Minnesota scores on direct snap

videos.description: Bulldogs QB Marcus McMaryion hooks up with TE Jared Rice on the bootleg to make it a 3-point game.
videos.headline: Fresno State cuts into lead with TD pass

videos.description: QB Marcus McMaryion lets one go and finds WR KeeSean Johnson along the sideline, who dives for the pylon and puts the Bulldogs up 14-13.
videos.headline: Fresno State takes the lead on 45-yard score

videos.description: Seth Green puts his head down and powers his way to the end zone, giving the Golden Gophers 21-13 lead late in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Minnesota WR uses legs to deliver go-ahead TD
